getAllActivitySchedule

public int[][] getAllActivitySchedule(int number)
Gets all activity schedule from the postgres/activity_schedule

Returns:
a integer 2d array (number of activity schedule * 8) contains:
1. id_schedule
2. activity_id
3. activity_purpose
4. start_time
5. end_time
6. travel_mode
7. individual_id
8. week_mode (1: weekdays 2: weekend)

getPopulationSchedule

public int[][] getPopulationSchedule(int number)
Gets all starts and ends of an activity schedule id for each individual from postgres/synthetic_population

Returns:
a integer 2d array (number of individual * 5) contains:
1. id
2. diary_weekdays_start
3. diary_weekdays_end
4. diary_weekend_start
5. diary_weekend_end

getStatistic

public int[][] getStatistic()
Gets all statistic from activity_statistic table

Returns:
a integer 2 dimensions array of statistic value contains 10 columns: id_stats, travelTime, delta_travelTime, best_tt_diffMode_sameStartTime, best_mode, best_tt_sameMode, bestStartTime, sumIndividual_sameMode, sum_individual_diffMode, most_diffMode
